data.description: This home features old-world charm with high ceilings and large rooms. Freshly painted interior throughout with new flooring on the main floor and updated bathrooms. Other updated include light fixtures, a newer boiler, most of roof has been replaced and some windows have been replaced. Huge full basement and outdoor space perfect for entertaining with plenty of on-street parking. Close to restaurants, bars, shopping on Carson St. and proximity to Birmingham Bridge makes for an easy commute. Across from Ormsby Park, Recreation center & pool.
